The bathroom was very clean and modern (I can't stand fusty old bathrooms), the bed was comfy, you get a desk with wireless access and TV, Microwave and Fridge.	The room itself was standard; clean, not particularly spacious, shower only, working TV, toiletries, coffee and free internet.	Also, the beds have down comforters, the bathroom is quite large, looks newly remodeled and has a great shower.	The bathrooms, equally compact, do offer plenty of shelf space, make up mirrors, hairdryers and Gilchrist and Soames toiletries.	The bathroom only had a shower and the closet was the size of a phone booth.